Database::Sophia
=============

DESCRIPTION

This is glue for Cassandra C/C++ Driver library.

Current beta5 ( https://github.com/datastax/cpp-driver/tree/beta5 )

See https://github.com/datastax/cpp-driver


INSTALLATION

Please, before install this module make Cassandra library.

Just follow the usual procedure:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


REPORTING BUGS

